{
  "stem": "9777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was crying more than I was eating.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then one day, we went to his aunt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And his aunt have a-- had a beautiful two-family homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were spacious and roomy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we got a whole room for ourselves-- and let me cook in the kitchen-- not that I'm a crazy cook.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she went to work, not realizing they are poor people too-- just they were lucky enough-- sold one house and bought another one.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we stood there for a few days and then went back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we got this apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Under the table, my husband paid $250 for the filth and cockroach-infested apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we actually belonged to the Joint, not to the HIAS, like my husband says.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the Joint from Park Row took care of us-- how much they took care of us-- gave us like $22 a week for food, for one or two weeks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they told us we should use up the money what we have on the passport, the $600.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So try to tell him that we had to pay the money for under the table, and for paint, and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't interested.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us $55 to buy two room of furniture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How could you buy two rooms of furniture?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The place they sent us to buy the furniture, we couldn't find.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was over a railroad tracks a-- a junk dealer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't find a house number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we never found the junk dealer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we bought a kitchen set.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a cousin gave us a crib.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we bought a bed for my son.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is what happened to the $55.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He tried.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
